import platform

from matplotlib import font_manager, rc
plt.rcParams['axes.unicode_minus'] = False

if platform.system() == 'Darwin':
    rc('font', family='AppleGothic')
elif platform.system() == 'Windows':
    path = "c:/Windows/Fonts/malgun.ttf"
    font_name = font_manager.FontProperties(fname=path).get_name()
    rc('font', family=font_name)
else:
    print('Unknown system... sorry~~~~')

conditionlist = [
    (apt['거래월'] <= 3),
    (apt['거래월'] <= 6),
    (apt['거래월'] <= 9),
    (apt['거래월'] <= 12)
]
quarterlist = ['1분기', '2분기', '3분기', '4분기']

apt['반기'] = np.where(apt['거래월']<=6, '상반기', '하반기')
apt['분기'] = np.select(conditionlist, quarterlist)

apt['평당거래금액'] = apt['거래금액'] / apt['전용면적(평)2']

apt['법정동'] = apt['법정동'].str.strip()

2. 10억 이상 매매 거래량

데이터 전처리¶

In [590]:
df_total = df.groupby(['거래월', '시군구명']).거래월.agg('count').to_frame('거래량')
df_billion = df[df['거래금액'] >= 100000].groupby(['거래월', '시군구명']).거래월.agg('count').to_frame('거래량')
df_total['유형'] = '총거래량'
df_billion['유형'] = '10억이상거래량'
df_vol = pd.concat([df_total, df_billion])

def draw(월):
    fig, ax1 = plt.subplots(figsize=(20, 10))
    ax2 = ax1.twinx()

    sns.barplot(data=df_vol.loc[월].reset_index(), x='시군구명', y='거래량', hue='유형', ax=ax1, palette='Purples')
    sns.lineplot(data=df_ratio.loc[월].reset_index(), x='시군구명', y='비율', color='slategrey', marker='o', ax=ax2)

# 시군구 (서울)
gdf_admin_gu = gpd.read_file('../data/SIG_202101/TL_SCCO_SIG.shp', encoding='euc-kr')

In [738]:
df_gu = df.pivot_table('평당거래금액', '시군구명')
df_dong = df.pivot_table('평당거래금액', ['시군구명', '법정동'])

gdf_gu = pd.merge(gdf_admin_gu, df_gu, how='left', left_on='SIG_KOR_NM', right_on='시군구명')
gdf_dong = dict()
for gu, code in options.items():
    gdf_dong[code] = pd.merge(gdf_admin_dong_dict[code], df_dong.loc[gu], how='left', left_on='EMD_KOR_NM', right_on='법정동')

def init():
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 8))
    gdf_gu.plot('평당거래금액', legend=True, cmap='PuBuGn', ax=ax)
    ax.set_title('서울시 자치구별 아파트 평당거래금액', fontsize=20)
    ax.set_axis_off()
    
    for index, row in gdf_gu.iterrows():
        xy = row['geometry'].centroid.coords[:]
        plt.annotate(row['SIG_KOR_NM'], xy=xy[0], horizontalalignment='center', verticalalignment='center')
    
def on_click(options):
    clear_output()
    display(dropdown)
    
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 8))
    gdf_dong[dropdown.value].plot('평당거래금액', legend=True, cmap='PuBuGn', ax=ax)
    ax.set_title(f'서울시 {dropdown.label} 행정동별 아파트 평당거래금액', fontsize=20)
    ax.set_axis_off()
    
    for index, row in gdf_dong[dropdown.value].iterrows():
        xy = row['geometry'].centroid.coords[:]
        plt.annotate(row['EMD_KOR_NM'], xy=xy[0], horizontalalignment='center', verticalalignment='center')

plt.figure(figsize=(7,7))

radii = np.array(df_empty_house['계']) / df_empty_house['계'].max()
